## Mentions & Hashtags Strategy

- **@mentions:** 2-3 per article. Only accounts genuinely referenced in the content. Wrap in `<a href="https://x.com/{handle}">@handle</a>`. Mentioned users get notified.
- **#hashtags:** 3-5 in a closing paragraph as plain text (auto-linked by editor). Mix niche + broad from SOUL.md hashtag pools.
- **External links:** `<a href="url">text</a>` for sources. Adds credibility.
- 🚨 Do NOT tag random big accounts for visibility — that is spam.
